==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Claver
<hw>Clav"er</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Frivolous or nonsensical talk;
prattle; chattering.</def> <mark>[Scot. & North of Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Emmy found herself entirely at a loss in the midst of their
<qex>clavers</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Thackeray.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Claviceps</ent>⟦br⟧
